      • createAssociation

        public Association createAssociation(String displayId,
                                     URI agent)
                              throws SBOLValidationException
        Creates a child association for this activity with the given arguments, and then adds to this activity's list of associations.

        This method first creates a compliant URI for the child association to be created. This URI starts with this activity's persistent identity, followed by the given display ID and ends with this activity's version.

        Parameters:
        displayId - the display ID for the association to be created
        agent - URI for the agent associated with this activity
        Returns:
        the created association
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if any of the following SBOL validation rules was violated: 12602, 12604, 12605, 12606

      • createUsage

        public Usage createUsage(String displayId,

                  throws SBOLValidationException
        Creates a child usage for this activity with the given arguments, and then adds to this activity's list of usages.

        This method first creates a compliant URI for the child usage to be created. This URI starts with this activity's persistent identity, followed by the given display ID and ends with this activity's version.

        Parameters:
        displayId - the display ID for the usage to be created
        entity - URI reference to the entity used
        Returns:
        the created usage
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if any of the following SBOL validation rules was violated: 12502, 12503

      • addWasInformedBy

        public boolean addWasInformedBy(Activity activity)
                         throws SBOLValidationException
        Adds the URI of the given Activity instance to this Activity's set of wasInformdBy URIs. This method calls addWasInformedBy(URI) with this Activity URI.
        Parameters:
        activity - the Activity instance whose identity URI to be added
        Returns:
        true if this set did not already contain the identity URI of the given Activity, false otherwise.
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if the following SBOL validation rule was violated: 12407.

      • addWasInformedBy

                         throws SBOLValidationException

        Parameters:

        Returns:

        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - if the following SBOL validation rule was violated: 12407.

      • addWasInformedBy

        public boolean addWasInformedBy(String displayId,
                                String version)
                         throws SBOLValidationException
        Constructs a compliant activity URI with the given display ID and version, and then adds this URI to this activity's set of wasInformedBy URIs.

        This method creates a compliant activity URI with the default URI prefix, which was set in the SBOLDocument instance hosting this activity, the given display ID and version. It then calls addWasInformedBy(URI) with this Activity URI.

        Parameters:
        displayId - the display ID of the activity whose identity URI is to be added
        version - version of the activity whose identity URI is to be added
        Returns:
        true if this set did not already contain the given activity's URI, false otherwise.
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - see addWasInformedBy(URI)

      • addWasInformedBy

        public boolean addWasInformedBy(String displayId)
                         throws SBOLValidationException
        Constructs a compliant activity URI using the given activity display ID, and then adds this URI to this activity's set of wasInformedBy URIs. This method calls addWasInformedBy(String, String) with the given sequence display ID and an empty string as its version.
        Parameters:
        displayId - the display ID of the activity whose identity URI is to be added
        Returns:
        true if this set did not already contain the given activity's URI, false otherwise.
        Throws:
        SBOLValidationException - see addWasInformedBy(String, String)
